.Dd January 7, 2023
.Dt IGPIO 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm igpio
.Nd Intel GPIO Controller
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "igpio* at acpi?"
.Cd "gpio* at gpiobus?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
provides a
.Xr gpio 4
interface for the following Intel chipsets:
.Bl -tag -width autoselect -compact
.It Alder Lake-N
.It Alder Lake-P
.It Alder Lake-S
.It Baytrail
.It Cannon Lake-H
.It Cannon Lake-LP
.It Cedarfork
.It Coffee Lake-S
.It Denverton
.It Emmitsburg
.It Gemini Lake
.It Ice Lake-LP
.It Ice Lake-N
.It Jasper Lake
.It Lakefield
.It Lewisburg
.It Lynxpoint
.It Raptor Lake-S
.It Sunrisepoint-H
.It Sunrisepoint-LP
.It Tiger Lake-H
.It Tiger Lake-LP
.El
Support for Broxton and Cherryview is not enabled yet.
.Pp
The driver supports
.Dv GPIO_PIN_INPUT ,
.Dv GPIO_PIN_OUTPUT ,
.Dv GPIO_PIN_INOUT ,
.Dv GPIO_PIN_ININ ,
.Dv GPIO_PIN_PULLUP ,
.Dv GPIO_PIN_PULLDOWN ,
and interrupt capabilies
.Dv GPIO_INTR_POS_EDGE ,
.Dv GPIO_INTR_NEG_EDGE ,
.Dv GPIO_INTR_DOUBLE_EDGE ,
.Dv GPIO_INTR_HIGH_LEVEL ,
.Dv GPIO_INTR_LOW_LEVEL .
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr gpio 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver first appeared in
.Nx 10.0 .
